====== WENOEXT library ======

The weighted essentially non-oscillatory library was initially developed by
Tobias Martin at the University of Rostock. The method and its validation has 
been demonstrated in

[1] J. W. Gärtner, A. Kronenburg, and T. Martin, “SoftwareX Efficient WENO library for OpenFOAM,” 
    SoftwareX, vol. 12, p. 100611, 2020, doi: 10.1016/j.softx.2020.100611.
[2] T. Martin and I. Shevchuk, “Implementation and validation of semi-implicit WENO schemes using OpenFOAM®,” 
    Computation, vol. 6, no. 1, pp. 1–36, 2018, doi: 10.3390/computation6010006.

When using this work please cite the first citation [1] for the newest version and for using version v-0.1 [2]. 


---------------------------

Other contributors to this development are:

Ivan Shevchuk
Timofey Mukha
Jan Gärtner


